sentence: Among the underlying components of the S&P 500 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in BLK (Symbol: BLK), where a total of 4,878 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 487,800 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 64.6% of BLK's average daily trading volume over the past month of 755,240 shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $330 strike put option expiring October 16, 2015 , with 2,387 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 238,700 underlying shares of BLK.
